headline: Gibraltar Lowers 2025 Guidance on Market Softness, Stock Down
summary: ROCK slashes 2025 guidance on softer demand and timing issues, sending shares down 11.4% as sales, earnings and EBITDA targets have been cut.

headline: 2 Profitable Stocks Worth Your Attention and 1 We Ignore
summary: Not all profitable companies are built to last - some rely on outdated models or unsustainable advantages. Just because a business is in the green today doesn’t mean it will thrive tomorrow.
